NAME
       icontopbm - convert a Sun icon into a PBM image


SYNOPSIS
       icontopbm [iconfile]


DESCRIPTION
       This program is part of Netpbm(1).

       icontopbm  reads  a Sun icon as input and produces a PBM
       image as output.

       pbmtoicon(1), pbm(1)
